= fluid-blue

== Description

A theme for Wordpress. Compatible with Wordpress 2.7. See it in action at http://www.lunar-ocean.com

Original work by Srini: http://srinig.com/wordpress/themes/fluid-blue/ forked by Antoine Toulme mostly for his own use. 
Please donate to Srini if you like this theme.

== Installation

Download and place in your blog wp-content/plugins/fluid-blue folder.

